Class JsonObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • bg.tu_varna.sit.a4.fn22621660.json.JsonValue
      • bg.tu_varna.sit.a4.fn22621660.json.JsonObject

  • public class JsonObject
extends JsonValue
    The JsonObject class represents a JSON object. It extends the JsonValue abstract class. It allows storing key-value pairs where values can be various JSON types (JsonValue instances).
